<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-contract text-danger me-2"></i>Terms & Conditions
      </h2>

      <p class="text-muted">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <p class="lead text-secondary">
        Welcome to StayNest. By using our platform, creating an account, publishing listings, making bookings, or submitting reviews, you agree to follow these Terms and Conditions.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-4">

      <h4 class="fw-bold">User Responsibilities</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary">
        Users are responsible for providing accurate information while creating accounts, adding property listings, making bookings, and submitting reviews. Any misleading or false information may result in account restrictions.
      </p>

      <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Listing Guidelines</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary">
        Property owners must ensure that listing details, images, prices, and descriptions accurately represent their accommodation. StayNest reserves the right to remove listings that violate platform guidelines.
      </p>

      <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Bookings and Payments</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary">
        Users must provide valid booking information and complete payments through authorized payment methods. Booking confirmation depends on successful payment verification.
      </p>

      <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Reviews and Content</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary mb-5">
        Reviews should be genuine, respectful, and based on actual experiences. StayNest may remove content that violates community standards.
      </p>

      <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark px-4 py-2 rounded-3">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>